## §3. COMPUTE SIDE — Resonance Engine

### §3.1 Input — EventEnvelope v2

```typescript
interface EventEnvelope {
  event_id: string;           // UUID v7 (time-ordered)
  causation_id: string | null; // parent event (LAW-1)
  origin_cell: string;         // cell phát signal
  origin_entity: PersonaSig;   // slot persona_signature filled
  timestamp: ISO8601;
  payload: unknown;
  idempotency_key: string;     // same key = same outcome
  
  // NEW v2 — per SPEC_ONG_MAU v0.1:
  identity_shape_hash: string; // SHA-256 của path d SVG shape
  wavelength: {
    primary: string;   // hex color
    secondary: string; // hex color
  };
  qneu: number;
  shell: 'K'|'L'|'M'|'N'|'O'|'P'|'Q';
}

interface PersonaSig {
  persona: 'kim'|'bang'|'can'|'kris'|'phieu'|'boi_boi'|'thien_lon'|'thien_nho'|'na';
  anchor: 'natt.sira' | string;
}
```

### §3.2 Resonance matching — không if/else routing (LAW-2)

```
Cho Envelope E, candidate cell C có Z_C baseline:

1. Compute Z_E (impedance của envelope) từ:
   - payload entropy
   - persona shell level (K→Q)
   - wavelength overlap
   - causation depth

2. Compute match score:
   T(Z_E, Z_C) = bell_curve(|Z_E - Z_C|, σ = σ_u)   // §6.3
   
   Z_E = Z_C  →  T = 1.0  (hấp thụ hết)
   |Z_E - Z_C| >> σ_u  →  T → 0  (phản xạ)

3. Reflection coefficient:
   R(Z_E, Z_C) = (Z_E - Z_C) / (Z_E + Z_C)
   
   R > 0  →  envelope "nặng" hơn cell, vượt qua
   R < 0  →  cell "hút" envelope vào
   R = 0  →  matched perfectly

4. Outcome emerge từ (T, R) + fiber lifecycle state:
   T > 0.75  →  FALL (cell match, tạo TouchRecord)
   T < 0.20  →  DISSIPATE (tan trong field)
   0.20 ≤ T ≤ 0.75  →  OSCILLATE (loop → ISEU mark suspicious)
```

### §3.3 Output — TouchRecord + outcome

```typescript
interface TouchRecord {
  touch_id: string;
  event_id: string;          // source envelope
  cell_id: string;           // cell matched (null if DISSIPATE)
  fiber_strength: number;    // 0.00-1.00, hysteresis 0.20-0.75-0.05
  outcome: 'FALL'|'DISSIPATE'|'OSCILLATE';
  qneu_delta: number;        // change in cell QNEU
  resonance_score: number;   // T value
  reflection: number;        // R value
  timestamp: ISO8601;
  
  // uei_architecture fields:
  decay_rate: number;        // saturating decay λ
  gossip_tier: 1|2;          // local cluster | global weak-tie
}
```

### §3.4 Fiber lifecycle — hysteresis 0.20-0.75-0.05

Per uei_architecture:
```
State: DORMANT
  │
  ├── fiber_strength rises to 0.20 ─────→ State: EMERGING
  │
  State: EMERGING
  │
  ├── rises to 0.75 ────────────────────→ State: STRONG
  │
  State: STRONG
  │
  ├── drops to 0.05 ────────────────────→ State: FADING
  │
  State: FADING
  │
  ├── drops below saturating decay ─────→ State: DORMANT
```

Hysteresis prevent flapping — fiber "không nhảy" giữa states với noise nhỏ.

### §3.5 Integration với Chromatic L1 (Kim wire)

Khi `outcome = FALL`, Resonance Engine emit signal vào Chromatic L1:
```
FALL → chromatic.tag(touch.cell_id, touch.resonance_score)
     → cell gắn màu (signature gắn màu)
     → L0 pheromone broadcast (hệ dắt ngược §14 SPEC_NEN)
```

Kim scope Phase C.2 (ROADLOAD v2).

