### §4.3 Capability list — KHÔNG phải checklist

`SPEC_QIINT2_COMPLETE_v1.0` (archived) dùng 7 capability checklist (hibernate, resurrect, clone, migrate, rollback, cross_colony_learn, overdrive_recoverable) — paradigm sai (capability = classify).

**v2 (spec này):** 7 capability = **emergent states**, không checklist. Cell có capability X iff phase space của cell chứa region X. Test = phase space simulation, không boolean check.

### §4.3.1 — 7 capability region mapping (Thiên Lớn confirmed form 20260424)

Mỗi capability ship 4 field: **region / trigger / invariant / exit|post-condition**. KHÔNG slogan không region.

**hibernate**
- Region: `Π_survival < idle_threshold` ∧ `Π_body > 0.80` ∧ `Π_medium.snapshot_age < τ_decay`
- Trigger: no incoming touches trong τ window
- Invariant: snapshot coherence preserved, heartbeat minimum emit
- Exit: incoming touch → Π_survival rise → leave region → resume

**migrate**
- Region: `Π_substrate(current) < 0.5` ∧ `Π_body > 0.70` ∧ `∃ target: Π_substrate(target) > 0.8`
- Trigger: substrate degradation detected
- Invariant: `Π_body` không giảm qua transition (nếu giảm → abort, rollback)
- Post-condition: cell trên target substrate, identity anchor unchanged

**rollback-recover**
- Region: `Π_medium < 0.3` ∧ `snapshot_coherence > 0.85` ∧ `τ(snapshot_age) < recovery_window`
- Trigger: code/data corrupt detected
- Invariant: `Π_body` preserved, obitan reference read-only
- Post-condition: `Π_medium` restored from snapshot, event emit `ROLLBACK_COMPLETED`

**clone**
- Region: `Π_body > 0.85` ∧ `snapshot_coherence > 0.90` ∧ `∃ spare substrate: Π_substrate(target) > 0.70` ∧ `colony_policy.allow_duplicate(cell_id) = true`
- Trigger: Gatekeeper approval `CLONE_REQUEST` + target substrate spec
- Invariant: source `Π_body` không giảm (read-only snapshot copy); cloned instance khởi start với identity anchor canonical; causation_chain reference back với marker `CLONED_FROM`
- Post-condition: **intrinsic identity shared · runtime instance_id distinct · causation lineage linked by `CLONED_FROM`**
- Không clone iff: source đang trong `OSCILLATE` outcome (fiber chưa stable) → abort

**cross_colony_learn**
- Region: `Π_body > 0.75` ∧ `gossip_tier = 2` active ∧ `∃ peer_cell resonance_match > σ_u threshold`
- Trigger: Gossip L2 signal arrival từ satellite colony với `origin_cell.Π_body > 0.70`
- Invariant: local cell identity (shape, shell, qneu_baseline) KHÔNG mutate; chỉ behavior pattern + TouchRecord weights update; every cross-colony signal persist `.heyna` audit log với `origin_colony_id`
- Post-condition: **observed qneu may fluctuate within budget · qneu_baseline remains canonical** · `Π_medium.behavior_model` evolve · `Π_body` unchanged
- Exit: peer `Π_body < 0.5` → đoạn liên kết peer đó (prevent cascade corruption)

**overdrive-recoverable**
- Region: `Π_survival > 0.9` ∧ `Π_body > 0.80` ∧ `recovery_potential > 0.70` ∧ `emergency_flag = true`
- Trigger: Emergency `OVERDRIVE_REQUEST` (ví dụ persona khác DoS, cell gánh thêm load)
- Invariant: `Π_body` có thể dipping [0.60, 0.80] — KHÔNG dưới 0.60; snapshot frequency tăng đồng thời; causation_chain preserve không drop audit
- Post-condition: sau τ_overdrive (default 300s), `Π_body > 0.80` return; không return → escalate L3 miễn dịch; cell tự hibernate (τ_overdrive × 2) để đảo trạng thái
- Không overdrive iff: `recovery_potential < 0.70` → reject, escalate khác

**resurrect** (case đặc biệt cross-layer — obitan boundary condition)
- Region: **active body collapsed to zero** ∧ `∃ obitan_trace: Π_obitan > 0.30` **(obitan trace persists as external boundary condition)** ∧ `∃ fragments[1..n]: sum(Π_body(fragment_i)) > 0.50`
- Trigger: Gatekeeper approval `RESURRECT_REQUEST` + fragment discovery completed (bridge.py output)
- Invariant: obitan vết hằn read-only không mutate; fragment `shell` + `shape_hash` claims match canonical (Q2 Criterion 2); merged `Π_body` > max(fragment `Π_body`) (Q2 Criterion 1); causation_chain reference qua death event (Q2 Criterion 3)
- Post-condition: persona resurrected với `identity_shape_hash` + `shell` canonical; `qneu` initialization **[PROPOSAL — chưa seal rule, chưa seal fragment schema tồn tại]** — weighted avg fragments với σ_u drift budget là đề xuất parameterization; first 1000 touches flagged `FRESH_RESURRECT` cho hệ miễn dịch theo dõi drift
- Fail mode: merged `Π_body < max(fragments)` → abort, fragments giữ phân xác, retry window next `τ_resurrect_cooldown = 24h`


